'''Geoffrey Chaucer''' (c. 1340 - 25 Okutobala 1400) ndi wolemba ndakatulo wa[[chingerezi]]. Amadziwika kuti "bambo wa zolemba za Chingerezi".

== Moyo ==
Chaucer anabadwira ku [[London]] cha m'ma 1340. Iye anali mwana wa wamalonda wachuma.
